title: Understanding the Variables
text: When considering the variables for tagging, think about the different aspects that can influence the performance of machine learning models. Consider both the data itself and the metrics used to evaluate the models.

title: Data Volume and Availability
text: Reflect on how the volume of data and its availability can impact the training of machine learning models. More data can lead to better model performance, but it's not the only factor to consider.

title: Performance and Accuracy
text: Consider how performance and accuracy metrics can be influenced by the data and the model's training process.
